org.opends.server.backends.jeb.importLDIF

Interface IndexOutputBuffer.ComparatorBuffer<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - object to use in the compare
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IndexOutputBuffer.IndexComparator
    Enclosing class:
    IndexOutputBuffer

    public static interface IndexOutputBuffer.ComparatorBuffer<T>
    Interface that defines two methods used to compare keys used in this class. The Comparator interface cannot be used in this class, so this special one is used that knows about the special properties of this class.
